<div class="header">
                Distance<div class="close-modal close-x"></div>
</div>
<div class="body">
<p>Use Distance Search to find Ads based on where you are and how far you want to travel.</p>
<label for="DistanceModalAddress">Location <span>(postal code or address):</span></label>
<input id="DistanceModalAddress" name="address" req="" title="Address" type="text" value=""/>
<label for="DistanceModalRadius">Search radius</label>
